{
  "stem": "54.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the only chance was when we could see somebody is during the day when we worked in the same-- you know, in the same factory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But unfortunate, not all of us worked in the same one, because they had different departments, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Other factories, they did-- they used to do other-- other, you know, kind of work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I made those-- those little bullets for the shotguns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Other people made different bullets, you know, bigger ones, maybe for the-- bombs for the airplanes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was going on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were working and working and working, in this was going one like this for-- until the liberation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Until we start feeling something in camp, that something is fishy there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You used to-- they used to-- used to cut off the light, the lights in the-- in the-- in the barracks, you know, in the bungalows.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That they shouldn't see that we have light, they shouldn't know, because the Americans at that time knew every little place where they had the prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were flying around and circling around, you know, in camp, but they didn't bomb us because they knew that were camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had all the informations there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the same city, in Sulzfeld, there was next, not far from us, not-- I mean, not far from the factory where we worked, was there a camp from French prisoners.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they were not only-- they were free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Those prisoners were free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They could go out from camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They got packages from their parents, from-- from friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They send them in packages with food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But when we start feeling that the-- the air was changing, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't have light so often.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't have light every night in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
